00:01:01.590 --> 00:01:04.530
of the public consciousness.

00:01:04.530 --> 00:01:08.330
In that early time, accessibility
hurdles were really keeping people

00:01:08.330 --> 00:01:12.300
with disabilities from engaging
with the technical revolution

00:01:12.300 --> 00:01:18.840
and that is what motivated him to get
involved with website accessibility.

00:01:18.840 --> 00:01:22.060
