as an independent consultant both

00:01:33.380 --> 00:01:37.880
for private and nonprofit
businesses and organizations.

00:01:37.880 --> 00:01:42.630
He is a blogger, a podcaster,
and a public speaker.

00:01:42.630 --> 00:01:46.640
We are very excited to have
him here today for his Keynote:

00:01:46.640 --> 00:01:50.690
Open Source and accessibility:
Do it with us, not for us.

